nodes.text: CT-27-3555 was a cadet and a part of Bravo Squad.

When ARC trooper Commander Colt arrived to supervise the graduation tests of the clone cadets, Bravo Squad was the first team to take the Citadel Challenge. During this challenge, all the cadets, including this one, worked as a team and finished the course in record time.
This clone's armor number was 5 and he only appeared in the episode Clone Cadets.
